{"title":"The Scolarian Kettlexpress is a Made in India Touring Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/scolarian-kettlexpress-touring-bike/","date":1741784439000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-10.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-10.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Scolarian is a small-scale production bicycle company based in India. It specializes in making fixed, gravel, and touring bikes using chromoly steel. The brand just announced its all-new, no-nonsense <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/touring-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">touring bike</a>, the <a href=\"https://www.scolarian.com/touringbikes\" target=\"_blank\">Kettlexpress</a>. Let’s check it out…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-13.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-13.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.scolarian.com/touringbikes\" target=\"_blank\">Kettlexpress</a> (approx $1,233 USD) is Scolarian’s all-road touring bike, designed to be a reliable companion in the remotest of locations. The platform provides comfort, stability, and ergonomics.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-16.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-16.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-16.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-16.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-14.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-14.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-18.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-18.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-18.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-18.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The frame is made of Reynolds 525 and seamless cold-worked chrome-molybdenum alloy 4130 tubes, welded in Coimbatore, India. You can choose between drop-bar and loop bar for the bike. The loopbar version has trigger shifters for changing gears, while the dropbar version uses time tested bar-end shifters that can be run indexed or friction, especially useful when the drivetrain is dirty, worn, mismatched or you are in the middle of nowhere.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-12.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-12.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Scolarian Kettlexpress Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Reynolds 525 CrMo Double Butted Main Triangle</li>\n<li>Microshift mullet 2×10-speed drivetrain</li>\n<li>Juintech Hydraulic Brakes 180F/160R</li>\n<li>Goodyear TR connector 650B X 50C tires</li>\n<li>Luggage rack &amp; mudguard mounts</li>\n<li>Side kickstand included</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-11.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-11.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-6.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-6.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scolarian-Kettlexpress-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Build Spec:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Frame: REYNOLDS 525 CRMO DOUBLE BUTTED MAIN TRIANGLE, TA IS MOUNT</li>\n<li>Sizes: XS, S, M, L, XL,XXL</li>\n<li>Fork: CRMO UNICROWN FORK TA IS MOUNT</li>\n<li>Handlebar: SCW EZEElOOPBAR 710mm</li>\n<li>Grips: ERGON GP1 (L)</li>\n<li>Stem: SCRN Alloy Stem ±6°</li>\n<li>Saddle: SCOLARIAN COMMUTER SADDLE</li>\n<li>Seatpost: AL6061T6 350 X 27.2mm</li>\n<li>Brakes: JUINTECH DBI FULL HYDRAULIC BRAKES 180F/160R</li>\n<li>Shifter(R): MICROSHIFT XLE Xpress shifters (RIGHT)</li>\n<li>Shifter(L): MICROSHIFT Xpress shifters (LEFT)</li>\n<li>Crankset: FSA 46-30T / Black</li>\n<li>RD: MICROSHIFT XLE 11, Active Motion RD+ with clutch, Direct Cable Pull Design</li>\n<li>FD: MICROSHIFT 2x centos</li>\n<li>Cassette: MICROSHIFT XLE 11-40T 10 SPEED</li>\n<li>Chain: YBN S10 S2 CHAIN</li>\n<li>Hubs: SCW 32H SEALED BEARINGS / 6 BOLT</li>\n<li>Rims: WTB ST 25 TUBELESS COMPATIBLE*</li>\n<li>*tubeless tape, valve and sealant not included</li>\n<li>Axle front: 100/15mm/thread 1.5</li>\n<li>Axle rear: 142/12mm/thread 1.5</li>\n<li>Tyres: GOODYEAR Connector TR 650B X 50</li>\n<li>Tire Clearance: 650B x 50 (With fender)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.scolarian.com/touringbikes\" target=\"_blank\">Scolarian</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/scolarian-kettlexpress-touring-bike/\">The Scolarian Kettlexpress is a Made in India Touring Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"a9cef1377070895fbd0f68996ef2e28b3c6c9e6a8ce2c9716a683db6f7c635d0","category":"Cycling"}